Lovely Learning Layan

Layan is an Arabic name that means "soft" or "gentle". A timid Absol who spends most of her time with her nose buried in a good book, she struggles in making friends because of her fear of saying the wrong thing. As a result, she spends most of social interactions squeaking not a single word.

Speaking of, she's very soft, and might actually squeak if poked.
